import React, { FC } from "react"
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom"
import { Profile } from "../Profile/Profile"
import { ProfileNav } from "../ProfileNav/ProfileNav"
import { ProfileContent } from "./ProfileContent"
import { Bookmarks } from "../../components/Bookmarks/Bookmarks"

type props = {
  toggle: any
  postNews: any
}

export const Content: FC<props> = React.memo(({ toggle, postNews }) => {
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
        <Switch>
          <Profile />
          <ProfileNav />
          <ProfileContent toggle={toggle} postNews={postNews} />
          <Route component={() => <Bookmarks postNews={postNews} />} path="/Bookmarks1" />
        </Switch>
      </Router>

      {/* <Switch>
        <Route path="/Profile"> */}

      {/* </Route>
      </Switch> */}
    </>
  )
})
